==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: High-proof
<hw>High"-proof`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Highly rectified; very strongly alcoholic; <as>as,
<ex>high-proof</ex> spirits</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>So as to stand any test.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧We are
<xex>high-proof</xex> melancholy.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>High-raised</ent>⟦br⟧
